Package: NLPstudio
Title: Work On SEC EDGAR Filings Plus Other Perks
Version: 0.0.5
Authors@R: c(
    person("Francesco", "Grossetti", , "francesco.grossetti@unibocconi.it", 
    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5130-7745")))
Description: An R package providing a streamlined workflow for processing SEC filings data. It includes
  functions to efficiently convert raw JSON files into a quanteda corpus, along with a comprehensive suite of
  tools for advanced Natural Language Processing (NLP) analysis.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
